			"entries": [
				"As you succeed on a saving throw, you become {@condition invisible} and an illusory duplicate of you appears to fail the saving throw and undergo the effects. The double suffers a horrific fate of your own devising, the result of which leaves it dead or {@condition incapacitated}. The illusion may include minor environmental changes as a result of the duplicate's presumed actions, such as a broken window the duplicate appears to have fallen through.",
